@startuml UC-004: Submit Lab for Grading

title UC-004: Submit Lab for Grading
autonumber

actor Student
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Submission API\n(Elysia)" as API
participant "SubmissionService" as SubmissionService
participant "IPGenerator" as IPGenerator
participant "SessionService" as SessionService
database "MongoDB" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as Queue
participant "Queue Consumer\n(FastAPI)" as Consumer
participant "Grading Service\n(FastAPI)" as Grader

== Submit for Grading ==
Student -> Client: Submit lab answers
Client -> API: POST /v0/submissions

API -> API: Verify authentication (JWT)

API -> SubmissionService: createSubmission(submissionData)

SubmissionService -> DB: Fetch lab and part details
DB --> SubmissionService: Lab and part data

SubmissionService -> SessionService: Get student's lab session
SessionService -> DB: Fetch active session
DB --> SessionService: Session with Management IP
SessionService --> SubmissionService: Session details

SubmissionService -> IPGenerator: generateJobFromLab()

IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Generate Management IPs for all devices
IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Calculate VLAN IPs
IPGenerator -> IPGenerator: Build complete job payload

IPGenerator --> SubmissionService: Job payload with all device configs

SubmissionService -> DB: Create submission record (status: pending)
DB --> SubmissionService: Submission created

SubmissionService -> Queue: Publish grading job
Queue --> SubmissionService: Job queued

SubmissionService --> API: Submission created + jobId
API --> Client: 201 Created + jobId
Client --> Student: Submission received, grading in progress

== Grading Execution (Async) ==
Queue -> Consumer: Consume grading job
Consumer -> Grader: process_grading_job()

Grader -> Grader: Detect device types (SNMP)
Grader -> Grader: Initialize Nornir connections
Grader -> Grader: Execute tasks (ping, command, NAPALM)
Grader -> Grader: Evaluate test cases
Grader -> Grader: Calculate scores

note right of Grader: Progress updates sent\nvia callbacks (UC-005)

Grader -> API: POST /v0/submissions/result
API -> SubmissionService: storeGradingResult()
SubmissionService -> DB: Update submission (status: completed)
DB --> SubmissionService: Updated
SubmissionService --> API: Result stored
API --> Grader: 200 OK

@enduml
